      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"1. YOGEN BALE showed good early burn and was there until turning but swamped late to finish 6th at Richmond in a Mix 2/3. Tough to beat if on-song. 3. MR. IRRELEVENT showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing sixth (18.16) in a Grade 5 at this track. Key runner on best form. 2. MIGHTY TROJAN was always prominent from this same draw last time and boxed on well to place (22.75) in a Mix 3/4 over 400m at Bulli. Harder here but expected to feature again. 4. PRINCE SAL must be included in calculations.\",\"runners\":[1,2,4],\"exclusive\":false}",
